The '''Smallburrow''' family was a family of [[Hobbits]] from the [[Hobbiton]] area. They were amongst the lower classes of the society, and were acquainted with families like the [[Gamgee Family|Gamgee]]s and [[Cotton Family|Cottons]].<ref>{{RK|Scouring}}</ref>
